Underground Wellness presents The Second Opinion Series, The Digestion Sessions.


-EVERYTHING YOUR DOCTOR DIDN'T TELL YOU ABOUT DIGESTIVE PROBLEMS-

Our hand-picked team of 25 functional medicine doctors, naturopaths, bestselling authors, and real food chefs reveal how you can eliminate your digestive problems by finding the root cause, treating undiagnosed infections, identifying the best diet for you, and healing your gut, naturally.

------------------------------------

This release includes all the interviews, presentations and bonus content.
The presentations are available as video, audiobooks, powerpoint and transcript.
